AMP it up for the behind the scenes from the session Sara and I did of her ELECTRIFYING Surge cosplay!  She has a habit of starting cosplays just days before I’m scheduled to visit her—and turning out a masterpiece EVERY SINGLE TIME! This was yet another notch in her superb track record. I’m so honored that doing photos with me motivates her so strongly and that my camera is so often the first to chronicle her creations! 
.
.
Unfortunately the weather the day I was in town was horrid. Cold, rainy—it’s not supposed to do that out in the desert of Arizona!  We had to make it work so we shot inside her house just outside her laundry room 😂 I think we really made a lot out of a humble setting! 
.
.
